Package oogasalad.engine.view

Class ViewState

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.engine.view.ViewState
public class ViewState extends Object
Holds the internal state needed to manage the current view of the application, such as stage, current display, input keys, and game manager reference. Allows for toggling between screens/states by external classes such as the factory package.

Acts as a central, mutable state object that can be shared across internal view components. Is only accessible by the factory package to encapsulate the View's state from external view packages.

Author:
Aksel Bell, Luke Nam
